'''Harvey''' is the tech who helped Meredith present the 3-D printer.

==History==
While Meredith was presenting the fork she had printed with her new 3-D printer, Derek noticed that the tech, Harvey, had a facial twitch. After the presentation, Derek and Jackson went to Harvey and offered to fix his hemifacial spasm. He was reluctant, but they talked him into it with help from [[Richard Webber]].

The surgery was successful and afterward, Harvey looked at himself in the mirror in awe, expecting it to twitch as it had for the past 20 years. Derek happily told him that it wouldn't.

==Career==
Harvey sells 3-D printers and ink cartridges.
